{"tid":111231,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N套有深度/學到野/有反思既漫畫","createTime":"2017-02-07T09:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T11:02:58.000Z","uid":42119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b53e1a3ad95561f3965a5741ebd0af994fde78d8","tid":111231,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"一人N套有深度/學到野/有反思既漫畫<br />\n最好附解說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n<strong>詐欺獵人</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.hamreus.com:8080/ps2/Q/QZLR/18/seemh-106-e74e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.hamreus.com%3A8080%2Fps2%2FQ%2FQZLR%2F18%2Fseemh-106-e74e.jpg&h=f8cae4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學到好多金融詐欺知識同千術，每本最後都有文詳解各種案例，完全係深度版警訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>神槍少女</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.hamreus.com:8080/ps1/g/GUNSLINGER/13/seemh-208-935b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.hamreus.com%3A8080%2Fps1%2Fg%2FGUNSLINGER%2F13%2Fseemh-208-935b.jpg&h=389d84ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.hamreus.com:8080/ps1/g/GUNSLINGER/13/seemh-177-7f5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.hamreus.com%3A8080%2Fps1%2Fg%2FGUNSLINGER%2F13%2Fseemh-177-7f5d.jpg&h=a079feeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學到好多有關意大利文化同知識<br />\n又好睇，劇情有深度，觀星講獵戶座果度好感傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>末世殺手</strong>（松本次郎）<br />\n好血腥好暴力，表逹好深奧既哲學<br />\n主角係奇怪法律之下既復仇代行人，係一個充滿混亂既社會保持自我"},{"pid":"8289e04553ca9338e7b7caa7cc3a200161649dd7","tid":111231,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"魔法戰爭"},{"pid":"a502f894fadc486745b6e7ab9a61f44ec6646a81","tid":111231,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote