n我同意"},{"pid":"b901669da18bf74436c5b09a98ff5fff9957d71f","tid":111231,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見樓主認真推介，決定提下你<br />\n魔法戰爭知名伏作</blockquote><br />\n原本見樓主咁真心都想題下佢,不過有人接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過魔法戰爭都唔識好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係睇日本漫畫，冇乜留意動畫界（其實個POST都係講緊漫畫）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa3280df1823ddf111983b9633e682f791431d7","tid":111231,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2857ad8897fd779b059d602ed43c91fef90cde9c","tid":111231,"uid":35385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上果堆都冇解說既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登貼野不嬲係咁<br />\n你估係好野分享？其實係等有睇過套野啲人和應自high</blockquote><br />\n呢句真"},{"pid":"2f734e4dce018f1f3f2867be79e89fe0d81ffbc8","tid":111231,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"浦澤直樹-pluto<br />\n用第二個視點改篇手塚治虫既出名作品-阿童木中地上最大機械人篇,入面有唔少反戰既思想,講機械人既感情<br />\n<br />\n浦澤直樹-二十世紀少年<br />\n用唔同時間點講一班細蚊仔既遊戲同夢想同佢地既未來,好感覺到昭和年代個陣既日本<br />\n<br />\n死亡預告<br />\n反烏托邦社會,每個人都要接種疫苗,係18-24歲個陣有機會死亡,以維持國家既繁榮,主角係一位派發死亡通知既政府官員,每集都講下啲人收到通知之後既反應<br />\n<br />\n黃金神威<br />\n講明治時期日本北海道既阿伊努族既文化同動物之類,主線係講主角要搵個寶藏"},{"pid":"682352ffd87e130c3a45f12082f43956f553df0e","tid":111231,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見樓主認真推介，決定提下你<br />\n魔法戰爭知名伏作</blockquote><br />\n原本見樓主咁真心都想題下佢,不過有人接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過魔法戰爭都唔識好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係睇日本漫畫，冇乜留意動畫界（其實個POST都係講緊漫畫）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知,不過係動物台啲人對深度呢個字好敏感<br />\n一係就覺得動畫漫畫冇深度係啲人懶高檔先咁講,一係咩狗屎垃圾都話有深度<br />\n講伏野變膠post就冇人嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17e1e56d961d428c03dc6e517e1138f9fc522ef","tid":111231,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/07/232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg&h=b20c517b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真正學到野無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d02cdd5a115422d021bf867025b6d17d249e8d","tid":111231,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"第一時間諗起怪醫黑傑克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6059b62dc352c109fafafa8895fa9e2d0ce38599","tid":111231,"uid":4758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"晚安pungpung<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356c2ce0a1e3bab1ee806c24b99417bac6d85a10","tid":111231,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/07/232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg&h=b20c517b&s={SIZE}