ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係睇日本漫畫，冇乜留意動畫界（其實個POST都係講緊漫畫）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知,不過係動物台啲人對深度呢個字好敏感<br />\n一係就覺得動畫漫畫冇深度係啲人懶高檔先咁講,一係咩狗屎垃圾都話有深度<br />\n講伏野變膠post就冇人嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪膠化我個PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真回jor"},{"pid":"1ab692702a376671cd1f27fe63dea9cd63ce3fc3","tid":111231,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dm5.com/manhua-kuailerensheng/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dm5.com%2Fmanhua-kuailerensheng%2F&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAry7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bd71c79c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dm5.com/manhua-kuailerensheng/</a><br />\n<br />\n值得反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810821aeec332f08429ab16e622b3128615ad543","tid":111231,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:10:45.000Z","msg":"狼與香辛料"},{"pid":"9e875aca5f2598c0161a61f5a5ac5edad044aa66","tid":111231,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"夫妻<br />\n<br />\n如何打造和諧性生活"},{"pid":"e6997ef041fe612096a421e92c0237843c952763","tid":111231,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/07/232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F232418_2861bd0f4763f78988b1832595ad52df.jpg&h=b20c517b&s={SIZE}\" /></b